{"tid":2021313,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"當年有隻政治Game  唔知而家發展成點","createTime":"2020-05-17T15:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T08:10:06.000Z","uid":298038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e483790f8a2bfadbbf3ba74247bad5bc8de5a910","tid":2021313,"uid":298038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:54:00.000Z","msg":"當年有隻game<br />\n每個玩家都係扮演一個居民<br />\n地圖用現實既世界地圖<br />\n每個人都可以選擇出生地<br />\n亦可以係戰爭中貢獻戰力<br />\n可以組黨  可以辦報<br />\n透過選舉做總統  做央行行長<br />\n<br />\n由於地圖同現實一樣<br />\n當網上世界既國家版圖<br />\n被他國&ldquo;侵佔&rdquo;  民族意識會引新手入game<br />\n光復國土<br />\n<br />\n過左咁多年  已經唔記得game名<br />\n當年甚至有新聞<br />\n話有人為左隻game課金課到傾家蕩產<br />\n<br />\n當年咁矚目既game<br />\n唔知而家點呢"},{"pid":"1fec64eecf703148f99504a170a548cfdaf5de72","tid":2021313,"uid":298038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T16:07:25.000Z","msg":"有無人揾得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e5167ebcc639af80b1ca3535514058bd1fc56d","tid":2021313,"uid":33443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T20:24:48.000Z","msg":"erepublik?"},{"pid":"81b72781e676169bfe01f053e5def43ae280c43e","tid":2021313,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T20:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0335bbc56c6ca145e58a008d301d1c421bf7fac2","tid":2021313,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e5167ebcc639af80b1ca3535514058bd1fc56d","tid":2021313,"uid":33443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T20:24:48.000Z","msg":"erepublik?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T20:30:53.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"77f76735c6340a1f1c1aeb5d24e0ec365810cfb4","tid":2021313,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T20:45:08.000Z","msg":"每日打工會送一個麵包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl